      "properties": {"text": ""},
      "widgets_values": [
        "CharacterPose PoC (Phase 0)\n\nModels:\nIf ComfyUI reports Missing Models on open, use Missing Models / Download — links are embedded in this workflow (HF direct).\nExpected folders: models/checkpoints, models/controlnet, models/clip_vision, models/ipadapter.\n\nCustom nodes (via Manager):\n- comfyui_controlnet_aux (DWPreprocessor)\n- ComfyUI_IPAdapter_plus\n\nUsage:\n1. Load character sprite in node 2 (identity reference).\n2. Load a target pose photo OR an OpenPose skeleton image in node 3.\n3. Adjust IP-Adapter weight (0.6-0.85) and ControlNet strength (0.7-0.95).\n4. Queue prompt and check identity retention + pose change.\n\nAfter validation, use CharacterPose custom nodes instead of this manual graph."
      ]
